{"tid":2054749,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞改口籲戴布口罩防武肺","createTime":"2020-06-07T11:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T11:56:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff60a2bde669b76e878570c8c7f4f55bd53938d","tid":2054749,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200607/4QPBDV2X5OHGFOS2CQG3HIY3YE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200607%2F4QPBDV2X5OHGFOS2CQG3HIY3YE%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUqDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=63e3dc44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200607%2F4QPBDV2X5OHGFOS2CQG3HIY3YE%2F&h=635de666\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200607/4QPBDV2X5OHGFOS2CQG3HIY3YE/</a><br />\n<br />\n世衞改口籲戴布口罩防武肺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZAXX6NZ7CL7L54FFOA75FQHXBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZAXX6NZ7CL7L54FFOA75FQHXBE.gif&h=6bec03f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世衞改口建議公眾戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n世界衞生組織（WHO）總幹事譚德塞前日改口，建議各地政府鼓勵大眾戴布口罩，「尤其在病毒廣泛擴散之處，以及難以實施社交距離的地方」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱按近期研究改指引<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞指，在有社區傳播的地方，「建議60歲或以上人士和長期病患者，如無法實施社交距離，就應戴上口罩」；世衞同時改口稱，即使設施內沒有已知的武肺患者，所有臨床醫護人員或照顧中心的員工任何時間亦應戴上外科口罩。有別於早前指，只有照顧武肺患者的醫護和照顧者才應戴外科口罩。世衞指新指引是基於近期研究顯示的證據。<br />\n<br />\n另外，世衞亦就非醫療級別的布口罩發放新指引，建議布口罩至少要<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n，如聚丙烯不織布；外層應是防水物料如尼龍。<br />\n<br />\n世衞緊急項目負責人瑞安強調布口罩只能減低佩戴者傳染他人的機會，而非防止佩戴者受感染。譚德塞強調單是戴口<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n我們所知的有效抗疫手法。」<br />\n法新社/美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"ba25f6df016d48244c6f7158225ffd5c54a86bd0","tid":2054749,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"世衛訓左幾耐"},{"pid":"af8829e0aebae578b34be0d14366ddefce5b2595","ti